<HEADLINE>
<P>
BETTING WITH SURELOCK: THE SILICON SLEUTH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
What should have been one of SURELOCK's best days ever fizzled after the eighth 
race when Tight Spot was disqualified from first to 10th, ruining a $40 exacta. 
</P>
<P>
However, the computer still showed a $47 profit for the day. 
</P>
<P>
The computer's bet today is a $10 exacta box, Majestic Moment-Decidedly 
Ragtime-Boldly Excellent, in the eighth. 
</P>
<P>
SURELOCK's Sun. Bankroll $1,795 
</P>
<P>
Sunday's Profit $47 
</P>
<P>
Current Bankroll $1,842 
</P>
<P>
Janice Goldinger lost $50 when Ladies Don't Lie proved false in the fourth race 
and Ono Gummo failed in the ninth race. Janice's bet is $15 to win and place on 
Golden Hope and a $10 exacta box, Golden Hope-Pictorial, in the eighth. 
</P>
<P>
Janice's Sun. Bankroll $1,579.75 
</P>
<P>
Sunday's Loss $50 
</P>
<P>
Current Bankroll $1,529.75 
</P>
