<P>
ORANGE COUNTY -- POLITICS; CALIFORNIA -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; LEGISLATORS -- 
ORANGE COUNTY; REPUBLICAN PARTY (ORANGE COUNTY); LEGISLATION -- CALIFORNIA; 
CALIFORNIA ASSEMBLY; TOLL ROADS; CALIFORNIA -- BUDGET 
</P>
