<TEXT>
<P>
To satisfy surging interest in Saudi Arabian weather among family and friends 
of American soldiers, the Weather Channel cable network has added a focus 
report on the region to its regular coverage, a network official said. 
</P>
<P>
Reports on Persian Gulf weather will be given twice each hour. 
</P>
