<TEXT>
<P>
Tammy Bakker hopes visitors to Disney World will join her new flock at an 
industrial complex nearby after going on the rides at the theme park. 
</P>
<P>
The wife of imprisoned TV preacher Jim Bakker held her first service at the 
industrial site Sunday after winning a zoning battle with the help of the 
American Civil Liberties Union. 
</P>
<P>
The Bakkers' fall from grace and her husband's fraud conviction for bilking 
followers of his PTL ministry made Mrs. Bakker pessimistic about the zoning 
fight. 
</P>
