park where her ministry has its TV recording studios. ACLU attorneys argued 
that the ban was unconstitutional. 
</P>
<P>
Mrs. Bakker said she may hold services on Friday evenings to attract visitors 
leaving Disney World. 
</P>
<P>
Her husband is serving a 45-year term in federal prison. 
</P>
<P>
The Bakkers set up an Orlando-based cable TV ministry before his conviction 
last year. 
